annotations.title: Temperance Grapefruit Collins a fantastic No-ABV cocktail for you teetotalers

textContent:
2oz (60ml) Grapefruit Juive
1oz (30ml) Lime Juice
.5oz (15ml) Simple Syrup
Top Soda Water

Shake and pour over ice in a collins glass
